{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-03e_149", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Lettre XXI"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Extraordinaire du Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", quartier de janvier 1678 (tome I), p. 149-151."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Lettre XXI."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À Paris. "}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "APres avoir consideré vos Enigmes, j’ay crû, Monsieur, que la premiere ne signifie autre chose que cet illustre & sçavantissime Corps de "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "l’Académie Françoise"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": ", composé de quarante doctes Chefs de diverse qualité, sçavoir, Ducs & Pairs, Evesques, Presidens, Conseillers, Ecclesiastiques, & Gens d’épée. Si j’ay deviné le Mot, il suffira pour moy ; J’auray le plaisir de voir les belles Explications que les Sçavans vous en auront données. Je trouve que la seconde Enigme nous cache "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "le Soleil"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[3]", "text": ". Je vous en donne l’Explication en ce Sixain."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’Enigme qu’un beau Quatrain fonde,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Cache sous un nuage un Astre sans pareil,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Assurément c’est le Soleil,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui sans vie, & bien loin des quatre parts du Monde,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "D’un mouvement reglé poursuit son premier cours."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy que sans vouloir voir, il regarde toûjours."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou si vous aimez mieux ces quatre Vers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vostre Quatrain Enigmatique"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Cache comme un nuage un Astre sans pareil."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Si j’en croy l’Esprit Prophétique,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Au travers des broüillards j’apperçoy le Soleil."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "L’Enigme en figure m’a embarassé. Je l’ay laissé à de plus habiles Gens que moy. J’en ay toutefois tiré une Explication que je me suis contenté de communiquer à quelques-uns de mes Amis, en attendant que vous nous en disiez le secret. Je suis, &c."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Desnes. "}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}], "attributes": {"rend": "border"}}]}